# Copy this file to `.env` (gitignored) and fill in the real value.
#
# EXPO_TOKEN — a personal Expo access token for a user that has access to the
# account/org set as `owner` in app.config.ts. Create one at:
#   https://expo.dev/accounts/<your-account>/settings/access-tokens
#
# When set, EAS CLI uses this token instead of your global `eas login` session,
# so THIS repo always builds under its own Expo account while other repos keep
# using whatever account you're logged into globally. The deploy and verify
# scripts in scripts/ load this file automatically. Never commit the real token.
#
# See docs/expo-account.md for the full setup.
EXPO_TOKEN=
